kr.ac.kaist.team888.region

Class Region

  • java.lang.Object
    • kr.ac.kaist.team888.region.Region

  • public class Region
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the region on the plane.

    A region is a square area of the plane, i.e., mathematically defined by [minX, maxX]Ã—[minY, minY]. This class uses those four values to determine a specific region.
